summary: Just wanted to share an example of... I don’t even know how to define it. This girl can’t stop hating on Brie Larson and Captain...
body:
Just wanted to share an example of… I don’t even know how to define it. This girl can’t stop hating on Brie Larson and Captain Marvel. Her videos are an example of someone who already has decided she will loathe the actress, but she continues to make videos about her anyway. Brie is a toxic feminist? What is going on??

Can anybody explain it to me? What’s the point in diminishing Brie, and then Carol, over and over again, comparing her to Gal Gadot, and WW, instead of being, ‘oh okay another female role model, nice!’ ? The comments section is full of validation for this girl (vast majority are dudes)

If it were a guy, I would get it. But that much hate from a girl? If she had done something really horrific and unforgivable, but she just made a movie and talks her mind? I must be really naive to think that women should support women… my bad.
